https://docs.rockylinux.org/guides/installation/
https://wiki.rockylinux.org/

repositórios extras:
habilitar repositórios do gnome-software
sudo dnf install --nogpgcheck https://dl.fedoraproject.org/pub/epel/epel-release-latest-$(rpm -E %rhel).noarch.rpm
sudo dnf install --nogpgcheck https://mirrors.rpmfusion.org/free/el/rpmfusion-free-release-$(rpm -E %rhel).noarch.rpm https://mirrors.rpmfusion.org/nonfree/el/rpmfusion-nonfree-release-$(rpm -E %rhel).noarch.rpm
sudo dnf config-manager --set-enabled crb

configurar dnf:
Para isso, abra um terminal e digite:
sudo nano /etc/dnf/dnf.conf
max_parallel_downloads=10
fastestmirror=true
deltarpm=true

zram
dnf install zram-generator

flatpak
$ sudo dnf install flatpak
$ flatpak remote-add --if-not-exists flathub https://dl.flathub.org/repo/flathub.flatpakrepo
$ reboot

+pacotes:
sudo dnf install  lm_sensors speedtest-cli vim neovim mc geany git curl testdisk ddrescue qphotorec smartmontools gsmartcontrol hwinfo lshw-gui htop yum-utils tmux tmate timeshift gnome-tweaks dia audacious gimp inkscape blender fish redshift ark filezilla arj cabextract p7zip lzip unrar unzip zip

mudar o shell:
sudo chsh -s /usr/bin/fish

habilitar o cockpit:
sudo systemctl enable --now cockpit.socket
sudo firewall-cmd --add-service=cockpit
sudo firewall-cmd --add-service=cockpit --permanent
sudo firewall-cmd --reload

